## Features

Monitor soil moisture, temperature, and humidity

Manage crop and irrigation schedules

Store readings in a SQLite database

Input validation and error handling

Logging with Python logging module

Observability/monitoring integration (e.g., Sentry)

Containerized with Docker & Docker Compose

API documented for easy integration

