## Testing

Run tests with:

docker-compose run tests

## Contributing and Making Changes

Create a new branch

git checkout -b improve-feature


Make changes on the codebase

Build and run with Docker to test

Commit changes

git commit -am "Improve Smart Farm feature"


Push to GitHub

git push origin improve-feature


Open a Pull Request

